Motherhood has changed my life in so many ways. I was never a girl who dreamed of being a mom growing up and until a few years ago I never had any interest of having children. I think that’s ok too, it’s not for everyone. 
I will say, I’m glad I opened that door when I was ready, it is the best gift I could have ever given myself. 
Experiencing that type of love is unlike any other. Motherhood has made me softer yet stronger. It’s made me enjoy the little moments as time is a thief. It has made my life more chaotic but also so fulfilled. I’m learning new things everyday and trusting my intuition as I know I was made to be her mother. 
Truly blessed 💗 #motherhood #motheranddaughter #mothersday #mylittlegirl

Meet our girl, Landry Brooke Adams 🎀 
Our tiny little dream come true. 
Our hearts are full and our family is complete.

Some kind of wonderful 🌈 one week with our LA Babe 🎀 Landry shares her bday with the greatest woman I know, my mama. 
She’s the sweetest, calmest little love (so far!) and big sister Della is adjusting well and loves to hold her every chance she gets. @russadams615 is the ultimate girl dad. Somehow he finds a way to make each of us feel loved and seen everyday. Lots of postpartum tears of happiness that I get to call this my life, my family is complete. 🩷#grateful
